>"},{"pid":"e61b2586379a396bea41e6190c5b5edfcf942124","tid":466911,"uid":10894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:07:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"307399e6c877e914536c01748b51a380518119b9","tid":466911,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:09:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有份屌達哥嗰啲出嚟講嘢未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩樣都有屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/130939_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F130939_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=61ced71f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1591ef8efea100cd80ddea5957af7f3b78c74a7","tid":466911,"uid":52418,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:13:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0795996d88c05330900020c0dc015a3e76435942","tid":466911,"uid":40932,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:15:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔該講東江水嗰啲唔好再妖言惑眾<br />\n邊個幫襯買東江水--香港政府<br />\n香港政府親中愛國關飲東江水咩事<br />\n水喉嚟到就係東江水<br />\n到你揀要水塘儲水定要東江屎水咩<br />\n<br />\n淘寶係你自己主動俾錢買<br />\n根本成個原理同邏輯都唔同<br />\n<br />\n利申返，跟關sir保達哥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n水都係主動買架啵！<br />\n東江水係政府買。<br />\n雖然水源來源有分水塘同東江水。<br />\n但大部分係東江水來。<br />\n<br />\n買東江水D錢邊到來？？？<br />\n唔好忘記大家都要交水費，根據用者自付原則，多用多繳費，少用少繳費.<br />\n咁已經都算主動啦。</blockquote><br />\n係喎，仲有主動交稅俾政府<br />\n我地應該全部辭職唔do<br />\n唔好益中共"},{"pid":"9f3b09cef2746920d16cedbe791a464faaed65b6","tid":466911,"uid":128178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:16:33.000Z","msg":"岩呀<br />\n睇緊東張西望就唔係睇緊tvb<br />\n唔睇膠劇果時就上連登話你班睇既係tvb打手"},{"pid":"80b9a731409f8d83a912cbfbbae0634dede810b0","tid":466911,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:18:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有份屌達哥嗰啲出嚟講嘢未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩樣都有屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/130939_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F130939_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=61ced71f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/131834_4a23f38842dfb956109d935702509218.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F131834_4a23f38842dfb956109d935702509218.jpg&h=9e0ae4b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c461554020a603e86eb2397d2bdfdb459c68100","tid":466911,"uid":10894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:22:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74653ccfbbe21cc5250904e5e15d997cd3a9ff54","tid":466911,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:24:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>所以各位應該第一時間斷停用香港食水。<br />\n因為香港食水好多都係來自東江水。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n水冇得㨂，淘寶有<br />\n<br />\n政府用你既錢買咩水控制唔到<br />\n<br />\n但你自己錢係咪益支那公司，係咪賣自己個人資料俾支共，係有得㨂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點會冇得揀？<br />\n1.選用外國品牌樽裝水。<br />\n<br />\n2.要求政府自建海水化淡廠，提供本地食水<br />\n<br />\n用方案1 頂返 三五七年。</blockquote><br />\n咁你357年唔駛沖涼喎"},{"pid":"b6afaa45d4b0d0feb904b654ba54c35ba141a638","tid":466911,"uid":52418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T05:25:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}